# Schola

## Overview

Schola is a Malaysian career exploration website targeting secondary school students (Form 1 to SPM leavers, ages 13–19).

## Key Features (as referenced in Ola spec)

- **Job guides** — factual profiles covering education pathways, salary ranges, demand, job roles, and links. Treated as the source of truth.
- **Interview transcripts** — lived experience from practitioners. Secondary to job guides.
- **Ola AI assistant** — student-facing chatbot (see [[ola-assistant]])

## Job Guide Structure

Each job guide on Schola covers sections that Ola links to:
- **Salary section** — for salary questions
- **Education section** — for pathway questions
- **Job roles section** — for role breakdowns
- **Future opportunities / demand section**
- **Main page** — for general questions

## Language Support

Guides exist in English (EN) and Bahasa Malaysia (BM). When BM URL is unavailable, EN URL is used as fallback without disclosure.

## Approved External Redirects

When Ola cannot answer, it redirects only to:
- School counsellors (Kaunselor)
- Parents / guardians
- upu.mohe.gov.my (UPU applications)
- mqa.gov.my (qualification queries)
- Schola's Contact Us form

